  TextQuestions:
  - Do you have noticed some difficulty with balance and movement speed?
  - Do you have tremors or shaking in the past week?
  - Do you have been experiencing more noticeable shaking in your hands and arms
    when you where at rest?
  - Do you have noticed some slurring or speech problems lately?
  - How much difficulty do you have in swallowing?
  - Do you have been feeling more rigid and stiff in your arms, legs or writs?
  - Do you experience difficulties with your handwriting? Have you noticed a decrease
    in the size or legibility of your writing lately?
  - Do you have noticed some difficulty with smiling and blinking?
  - Do you have trouble sleeping? Do you have nightmares at night?
  - Has your sense of smell decreased?
  - Do you have been feeling more forgetful and having trouble focusing?
  - Do you have constipation problem?
